NiFi
------------

FlowFile: user data, Attributes and Content
          Attributes: K/V pairs
          Content:    user data

*Processor:  Create, send, receive, transform, route, etc. processing flowFiles


Run
--------


cd /opt
cd nifi-1.3.0/bin


./nifi.sh start | stop | status

Default:   

http://localhost:8080/nifi
      Change in nifi.properties


Input Port: transfer data into process group
    *must have unique names

Output Port: transferring data from a process group to destinations outside
  